(Corrects company name in headline.)  Ibovespa falls 0.6% at 4:14pm in
 Sao Paulo .  DECLINERS:
* Embraer (EMBR3 BS) -5%; worst performance on gauge
* Fleury (FLRY3 BS) -2.5%; Omar Magid Hauache replaced as CEO
* Petrobras (PETR4 BS) -2.3%; co. said it doesn’t expect to
raise fuel prices  ADVANCERS:
* BR Properties (BRPR3 BS) +1.4%; co. agreed to sell real-estate
assets for 442m reais to a BTG Pactual fund
* Hering (HGTX3 BS) +1.9%;  Brazil ’s retail sales rose 1.9% in
July M/m vs. median estimate of a 0.2% increase
* PDG (PDGR3 BS) +3.6%
* OGX (OGXP3 BS) +2.6%; Brazilian exchange raised short interest
limit for co. to 50%  To contact the reporter on this story:
